{"tid":623510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【博鰲論壇】為中美貿易戰降溫 習：大幅放寬金融市場 增進口減關稅","createTime":"2018-04-10T04:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T05:14:44.000Z","uid":65328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4435d1ebee2bfdb11cec47a623ca2d6e469475e1","tid":623510,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180410/58054402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58054402&d=aPFo5rXQnvv5auJGqgD5WBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4fc9949c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58054402&h=d3457a57\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180410/58054402</a><br />\n<br />\n【博鰲論壇】為中美貿易戰降溫 習：大幅放寬金融市場 增進口減關稅<br />\n<br />\n博鰲亞洲論壇年會會場(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平，今早在博鰲亞洲論壇年會的開幕儀式上發表演說，罕有地在全國人大、政協兩會後再度作出經濟政策宣示，公佈了一系列開放市場措施，包括開放金融市場准入規定、擴大進口、降低關稅，似是要間接滿足美國對華貿易的要求，為連日來中美兩國貿易戰的熾熱局勢降溫。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在演講中表示，將大幅放寬市場准入，確保放寬銀行、證券及保險行業的外資股比限制的措施落實執行；加快保險行業開放進程，放寬外資金融機構設立限制，擴大業務範圍；在製造業方面，會放寬汽車製造業的外資股比例限制。<br />\n<br />\n習近平提到，會創造更吸引投資環境，加強與國際經貿規則對接，增加透明度，依法辦事，鼓勵競爭；上半年完成修訂外商投資負面清單工作。另外，中國會主動擴大進口，「不以追求逆差為目標，真誠希望擴大進口」。中國今年亦會相當幅度降低汽車進口關稅，同時降低部分其他產品關稅，希望發達國家停止人為設限，放寬對華高技術產品出口管制。"},{"pid":"9837b4b83f280871776e9b1814ab9927f6187d26","tid":623510,"uid":61280,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：奉陪到底，攪笑到最後！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8d0ecb601c70accc29b609fe21b432bd1d8c4962","tid":623510,"uid":10064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"又係得把口講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48eb20e21983fb7b277578e5f7a83ee15af45e","tid":623510,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0ecb601c70accc29b609fe21b432bd1d8c4962","tid":623510,"uid":10064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"又係得把口講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"支那認哂輸投降"},{"pid":"bbe39345376f160f928f0ecf8af56794f24847e2","tid":623510,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"拖下先啫，侵侵唔會信"},{"pid":"dab1fbf6644f5b336b3735c0fac74efc9124a173","tid":623510,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33c46a398c99d9758616ed060f320c07bf33de8","tid":623510,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef48eb20e21983fb7b277578e5f7a83ee15af45e","tid":623510,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0ecb601c70accc29b609fe21b432bd1d8c4962","tid":623510,"uid":10064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"又係得把口講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:02:2